      "text": "Proof-of-Cooperation does not implement any mining or minting functionality, which are both competitive systems. Instead, certified validation nodes (in short CVNs) cooperate to secure the network. Proof-of-Cooperation will be introduced with FairCoin2 in 2017, whilst keeping all balances from the old FairCoin1 network - [https://fair-coin.org/en/ecological-blockchain-consensus fair-coin.org]"
